<p style="color: #444444; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px;"> Dear driver, </p>

<p style="color: #444444; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px;"> Please find the information for your transfer below: </p>

<table style="width:500px; border:0; padding:0; color: #444444; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px;">


<tr>
    <td width="100px;" style="padding:5px 0;">For :</td>
    <td style="padding:5px 0;"><%=@service.first_name %><%=@service.last_name %></td>
</tr>
<tr>
    <td style="padding:5px 0;">From :</td>
    <td style="padding:5px 0;"><%=@service.pick_up_address %></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding:5px 0;">On :</td>
  <td style="padding:5px 0;"><%=@service.pick_up_date.strftime("%A, %d %b %Y")%></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding:5px 0;">At :</td><td style="padding:5px 0;"><%=@service.pick_up_date.strftime("%Ih%M %P")%></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding:5px 0;">Duration :</td>
  <td style="padding:5px 0;"><%=pluralize @service.number_hours_at_disposal.round, "hour" %></td>
</tr>
</table>

<p style="color: #444444; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px;">
  Please click on the link below, when your transfer is done: <br />
  <%= link_to "Confirm your transfer", confirm_service_url(@service) %>
</p>



<p style="color: #444444; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 20px;">Sincerly,<br />
Yours <%= @service.car.company.name%> team </p>
